      "V.  METHODOLOGY FOR BUSINESS VALUE ANALYSIS OF",
      "INNOVATIVE IT  IN A BUSINESS SECTOR",
      "The proposed methodology is structured in two main",
      "phases. The first phase focuses on planning the business value",
