      "Table 1. Populated Architecture Framework",
      "![Page 5, Figure 1](subjects/Ggo/T4. Recursos. Arquitectura empresarial/Practica AE 2024/Teaching Case Notes -with bios-images/Teaching Case Notes -with bios_page_005.png)",
