      "• Multi-Head Attention",
      "• Training and Inference of Transformers",
      "• Why Do Transformers Work So Well?",
      "• Applications of Transformers",
      "3. Transformer-based Language Models Architectures",
      "• BERT",
      "• GPT",
      "• BART",
